Yeah, she came sniffing
around my office this afternoon.

31:29.083 --> 31:30.416
Asking questions.

31:31.291 --> 31:32.291
About you.

31:33.416 --> 31:34.791
Keep her there.

32:05.041 --> 32:06.833
There was no wind that night.

32:08.458 --> 32:11.458
CO2 from one of your pipelines

32:12.500 --> 32:14.125
