named Louis Gagnon?

33:29.250 --> 33:30.250
Yeah.

33:31.958 --> 33:33.208
I can help you.

33:33.291 --> 33:36.500
Yeah, that's what
Dr. Bouchard said too.

33:38.541 --> 33:41.250
Just another fucking mighty
white woman coming along

33:41.333 --> 33:43.833
