what to do.

35:17.666 --> 35:20.708
I ain't fucking doing
anything you tell me to do.

35:21.166 --> 35:22.208
Fuck that.

35:34.791 --> 35:36.708
You're the only good thing
that's happened to me

35:36.791 --> 35:37.791
