if I'd heard anything.

48:53.458 --> 48:54.791
Holy fuck, Frank!

48:54.875 --> 48:56.375
His real name is Jack Devlin.

48:56.458 --> 48:58.708
He doesn't know me from Adam,
but he soon will.

48:58.791 --> 49:01.083
Jesus Christ, you said
you had a loose end to tie up,

49:01.166 --> 49:02.976
did that mean killing
the goddamn chief of police?

49:03.000 --> 49:04.375
I haven't got any choice, love.

49:05.000 --> 49:06.375
Frank, listen to me.

49:08.041 --> 49:09.708
I don't know what
your debt of honor is,

49:09.791 --> 49:11.625
and right now
I don't give a shit.

49:11.708 --> 49:13.708
And I'm telling you,
that man would sooner kill you

49:13.750 --> 49:14.767
than give you
the time of the day.

49:14.791 --> 49:15.791
