49:19.250 --> 49:20.250
Walk.

49:21.083 --> 49:21.958
Walk?

49:22.041 --> 49:23.521
I'll cover for you.
I'll buy you time.

49:25.833 --> 49:27.458
Walk out the back door,

49:27.541 --> 49:29.291
then keep walking
and don't turn back.

49:30.375 --> 49:31.750
And leave you in the lurch?

49:32.375 --> 49:33.583
No, I will join you.

49:33.666 --> 49:35.500
Yeah? And what about this place?

49:35.583 --> 49:36.726
This is bricks
and mortar, Frank.

49:36.750 --> 49:38.267
I'd rather lose this place
than lose you.

49:38.291 --> 49:39.791
No, I am not running!

49:41.666 --> 49:43.875
And that fucker has shat
on my dreams once before.

49:43.958 --> 49:46.625
I am not gonna let him
do it again. Do you hear me?

49:46.708 --> 49:48.083
I will take care of it.

49:49.791 --> 49:50.958
For us.

49:51.541 --> 49:52.791
And then we'll be free.

49:53.416 --> 49:55.267
Let me just go out there
and put him off the scent.

49:55.291 --> 49:56.125
Please, Frank, please.

49:56.208 --> 49:57.750
No, you're not gonna do
my dirty work.

49:59.833 --> 50:01.166
I'm gonna damn well try.

50:03.791 --> 50:05.125
You, fucking walk.

50:17.500 --> 50:18.875
Nothing happens in this town

50:18.958 --> 50:20.583
I don't find out
about sooner or later.

50:22.916 --> 50:24.541
If I get wind of anything,

50:24.625 --> 50:25.708
I'll let you know.

50:26.958 --> 50:28.291
Good. 'Cause...

50:30.041 --> 50:31.921
the men who tried to kill me,
they fucked it up.

50:32.791 --> 50:34.166
They killed my boy instead.

50:36.375 --> 50:37.375
He was only five.

50:39.208 --> 50:40.666
Five and half,
if you're counting.

50:53.041 --> 50:54.561
Is there something
you want to tell me?

50:57.875 --> 50:58.875
No.

50:59.041 --> 51:02.083
I just...
Like I said, I'll ask around.

51:15.333 --> 51:16.333
Who's your new friend?

51:19.625 --> 51:21.916
He's, the new partner.

51:22.000 --> 51:25.083
He's a backer, actually.
II still run this place.

51:26.250 --> 51:27.333
Mind if I talk to him?

51:29.958 --> 51:31.083
No, I'll go get him for you.

51:31.166 --> 51:32.366
That's all right, I've got it.

